<section class="privacy-policy container my-5">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Game Shop collects personal information about you when you interact with our website, products, and services. This includes information such as your name, email address, phone number, and payment details. We use this information to provide you with a better shopping experience, to process your orders, and to communicate with you about our products and services.</p>

    <h2>How we protect your information</h2>
    <p>We take the security of your personal information seriously and have implemented various technical and organizational measures to ensure the confidentiality and integrity of your data. This includes using secure connections, encryption, and limiting access to your data to only those who need it to perform their job.</p>

    <h2>How we use cookies</h2>
    <p>Game Shop uses cookies to personalize your experience on our website, to remember your preferences, and to analyze how you interact with our products and services. You can manage your cookie preferences by adjusting your browser settings, but please note that some features of our website may not function correctly without cookies.</p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>We use third-party services, such as payment processors and analytics providers, to help us deliver our products and services. These providers may collect information about you in accordance with their own privacy policies.</p>

    <h2>Contact us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about our privacy policy or how we use your personal information, please contact us at privacy@gameshop.com.</p>
</section>